title: Sidewall, ca. 1810
provenance: This paper was found in an old Connecticut house.
creditline: Gift of The Museum at The Fashion Institute of Technology
description: Central motif of parrot sitting on lace panel suspended from bunches of peacock feathers. This alternates with floral bouquet. Printed in varnished green, pink and white on yellow ground.
